ZH:礁石是海洋中的岩石。
EN: Reefs are rocks in the ocean.

ZH:礁石是海洋中生物的家园。
EN: Reefs are homes for marine life.

ZH:礁石在退潮时会露出水面。
EN: Reefs are exposed at low tide.

ZH:礁石提供了海底生物的食物来源。
EN: Reefs provide food for marine organisms.

ZH:礁石可以形成海滩。
EN: Reefs can form beaches.

ZH:礁石受海浪侵蚀。
EN: Reefs are eroded by waves.

ZH:礁石上生长着很多珊瑚。
EN: Reefs are covered in coral.

ZH:礁石有不同形状和颜色。
EN: Reefs come in different shapes and colors.

ZH:礁石有时会被船只撞上。
EN: Reefs are sometimes hit by ships.

ZH:礁石也可以成为水下潜水点。
EN: Reefs can also be diving spots.

ZH:礁石的生长需要长时间。
EN: Reefs take a long time to grow.

ZH:礁石提供保护，减少海浪的冲击。
EN: Reefs provide protection and reduce wave impact.

ZH:礁石是海洋生态系统中重要的组成部分。
EN: Reefs are important components of marine ecosystems.

ZH:礁石上有很多海洋动物。
EN: Reefs are home to many marine animals.

ZH:礁石的颜色会随着季节变化而改变。
EN: The color of reefs can change with the seasons.

ZH:礁石是潜水爱好者的天堂。
EN: Reefs are paradise for scuba divers.

ZH:礁石上能见到五颜六色的鱼类。
EN: Colorful fish can be seen on reefs.

ZH:礁石被誉为海底花园。
EN: Reefs are called the underwater garden.

ZH:礁石的形状各异。
EN: Reefs come in various shapes.

ZH:礁石能够保护沿岸地区免受海侵。
EN: Reefs can protect coastal areas from erosion.
